title: 3Ball MTY.2014.GLOBALL.[Mp3].320Kbps.-ROSTROMASCARADO
description:
2014 album from the Mexican artists.The worldwide phenomenon 3BallMTY is back with their sophomore release GLOBALL. The DJs and producers native of Monterrey Mexico, innovate their sounds with collaboration from artists like Far East Movement, Belinda, Gerardo Ortiz, El Bebeto, America Sierra, Becky G and many more. The album features 12 songs including the already released tracks ''Quiero Bailar (All Through the Night)'' ft. Becky G and ''La Noche es Tuya'' ft. Gerardo Ortiz & America Sierra as well as the smash hit ''Vive Hoy''; theme song of the Pepsi Hispanic summer campaign in 2012.
